## Context

The Research Data Journal for HSS returned a revise-and-resubmit decision on
manuscript RDJ-26561, "A Curated Corpus of Climate Finance Literature,
1990–2024" (`deliverables/data-paper/data-paper.qmd`). Coeditor Cédric Chambru,
one referee report (two other invited referees never delivered). Editor:
"close to being suitable for publication"; deadline **three months from the
decision letter** — treat as due ~2026-10-20, email the editor if slipping.

Sources are archived with text sidecars at
`~/CNRS/papiers/sent/RDJ4HSS_Curated_Corpus_Climate_Finance/2026-07-20 decision/`
(decision letter `rdj_26561_DLTR`, referee report `rdj_26561_report_1`).
The remark ledger mapping every remark to a child ticket is
`deliverables/data-paper/revision-rdj26561/ledger.dedup.jsonl` (15 distinct
remarks; coverage check clean at filing time).

## Children

- 0275 — OpenAlex limitations and pipeline robustness discussion (ED-01, R1-11, R1-16b)
- 0276 — deduplication: discussion, WP-vs-published weakness, per-procedure counts (ED-01, R1-12)
